      "guidanceId": "css",
      "guidanceCategory": "css",
      "severity": "high",
      "confidence": "high",
      "summary": "Fixed 1200px layout overflows a narrow mobile viewport.",
      "evidence": "At an emulated 360x800 viewport the layout primitive reported horizontal overflow of 1158px (document scrollWidth far exceeds visualViewport.width 360); a screenshot at 360px shows the blue .fl-hero (computed width ~1264px) clipped off-screen. The hero and body hard-code width: 1200px.",
      "suggestedFix": "Replace the fixed width: 1200px with width: 100%; max-width: 1200px; box-sizing: border-box so the layout adapts down to small screens.",
      "effort": "small",
      "scenario": "fixed-layout",
      "artifacts": [
        "evidence/fixed-layout-360.png"
