      "guidanceCategory": "user-experience",
      "severity": "medium",
      "confidence": "high",
      "summary": "Reused component does not adapt to its container (no container queries).",
      "evidence": "An evaluate probe found the same .cq-card stays flex-direction: row inside the 240px-wide .cq-narrow container (cramping the 80px thumbnail against the text), and no @container rule or container-type is declared. The component responds only to the viewport, not its container.",
      "suggestedFix": "Add container-type: inline-size to the wrapper and a @container (max-width: 320px) rule that stacks the card (flex-direction: column; thumb width: 100%). See guidance id size-aware-styling.",
      "effort": "small",
      "scenario": "no-container-queries"
